      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag six-speed manual and a speed-sensitive M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal power delivery. This specimen is mechanically flawless, with a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains true to factory specifications. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield is in pristine condition, offering a tactile, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare. A concours-level vehicle for the discerning purist.",
